description.p:
(a) a drive unit having an electric motor and a drive shaft;


(b) a bearing eccentrically mounted on the drive shaft and located radially eccentrically relative to the drive shaft;


(c) a carrier plate mounted on the bearing and


(d) a platen for mounting on the carrier plate characterised in that the carrier plate is provided with a first engagement means and the platen is provided with second engagement means to engage with the first engagement means by rotation of the platen relative to the carrier plate.
